Interestingly, the Label and Location document at the FCC refers to the AX200D2WL and lists the FCC ID as AX200D2L and the IC ID as 1000M‚ÄêAX200D2L. The AX200 (Cyclone Peak 2) is supposedly descended from the 22260 (Cyclone Peak) which was never released . The 22260 was likely closely related to the 9260 (Thunder Peak).
